(154, '_site_transient_wp_plugin_dependencies_plugin_data', 'a:1:{s:14:\"contact-form-7\";a:35:{s:4:\"name\";s:17:\"فرم تماس 7\";s:4:\"slug\";s:14:\"contact-form-7\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"6.0.4\";s:6:\"author\";s:75:\"<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/takayukister/\">Takayuki Miyoshi</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:44:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/takayukister/\";s:12:\"contributors\";a:1:{s:12:\"takayukister\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:44:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/takayukister/\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:120:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/538487024e649d43dea84ff38d14582d03119e3e7aaaca3b7692443335999133?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:16:\"Takayuki Miyoshi\";}}s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"6.6\";s:6:\"tested\";s:5:\"6.7.2\";s:12:\"requires_php\";s:3:\"7.4\";s:16:\"requires_plugins\";a:0:{}s:6:\"rating\";i:80;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:1435;i:4;i:146;i:3;i:75;i:2;i:68;i:1;i:404;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:2128;s:11:\"support_url\";s:52:\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/contact-form-7/\";s:15:\"support_threads\";i:146;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:43;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:10000000;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:21:\"2025-02-18 6:51am GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2007-08-02\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:25:\"https://contactform7.com/\";s:8:\"sections\";a:6:{s:11:\"description\";s:3091:\"<p>Contact Form 7 is a plugin designed to be a practical tool for all WordPress users who embrace the philosophy of free and open source software. It employs sophisticatedly modularized architecture and its original <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/ SCHEMA-woven-validation/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Schema-Woven Validation</a> technology.</p>\n<h4>مستندات و پشتیبانی</h4>\n<p>می‌توانید <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/docs/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">اسناد</a>، <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/faq/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">سؤالات متداول</a> و موارد دیگر را پیدا کنید. اطلاعات دقیق درباره فرم تماس 7 در <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">contactform7.com</a>. هنگامی که نمی توانید پاسخ سؤال خود را در سؤالات متداول یا در هر یک از اسناد پیدا کنید، <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/ PLUGIN/contact-form-7/\" rel=\"ugc\">تالار گفتمان پشتیبانی</a> را بررسی کنید. a> در WordPress.org. اگر نمی توانید موضوعی را که به موضوع خاص شما مربوط می شود پیدا کنید، موضوع جدیدی برای آن ارسال کنید.</p>\n<h4>فرم تماس 7 به حمایت شما نیاز دارد</h4>\n<p>It is hard to continue to maintain this plugin without support from users like you. There are several ways for you to <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contributing/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">contribute to the project</a>: testing, coding, translating it into your local languages, helping other users, financial donations, etc, etc. We equally welcome you regardless of the way you contribute.</p>\n<h4>توجه به حریم خصوصی</h4>\n<p>با پیکربندی پیش فرض، این افزونه، به خودی خود، موجو نیست:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>پیگیری پنهانی کاربران؛</li>\n<li>نوشتن هر اطلاعات شخصی کاربر در پایگاه داده؛</li>\n<li>هر گونه اطلاعات را به سرورهای خارجی ارسال کنید؛</li>\n<li>استفاده از کوکی‌ها.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>اگر ویژگی های خاصی را در این افزونه فعال کنید، اطلاعات شخصی ارسال کننده فرم تماس، از جمله آدرس IP او، ممکن است به ارائه دهنده خدمات ارسال شود. بنابراین، تایید سیاست حفظ حریم خصوصی ارائه دهنده افزونه  توصیه می شود. این ویژگی ها عبارتند از:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>reCAPTCHA (<a href=\"https://policies.google.com/?hl=en\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Google</a>)</li>\n<li>اکیسمت (<a href=\"https://automattic.com/privacy/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Automattic</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.constantcontact.com/legal/privacy-center\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Constant Contact</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.brevo.com/legal/privacypolicy/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Brevo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://stripe.com/privacy\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Stripe</a></li>\n</ul>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:601:\"<ol>\n<li>پوشه <code> contact-form-7 </code> را به پوشه <code> / wp-content /plugins/ </code> بارگذاری کنید.</li>\n<li>افزونه را از مسیر <strong>افزونه ها</strong> بخش (<strong>افزونه ها &gt; افزونه های نصب شده</strong>) فعال نمایید.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>منوی <strong>Contact</strong> را در ادمین کنسول وردپرس پیدا خواهید کرد.</p>\n<p>برای مشاهده چگونگی عملکرد سری به <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">سایت افزونه</a> بزنید.</p>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:541:\"<p>آیا در مورد  فرم تماس 7 سؤالی دارید؟ از این کانال های پشتیبانی مرتبط استفاده کنید.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/docs/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\"> Docs </a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/faq/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\"> پرسش و پاسخ </a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/ PLUGIN/contact-form-7/\" rel=\"ugc\">تالار گفتگو</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/support/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\"> پشتیبانی </a></p>\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:1962:\"<p>برای کسب اطلاعات بیشتر، <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/category/releases/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\"> انتشارات </a> را ببینید.</p>\n<h4>6.0.4</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-604/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-604/</a></p>\n<h4>6.0.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updates the copyright year to 2025.</li>\n<li>Updates the &#8220;Contact Form 7 needs your support&#8221; message content.</li>\n<li>Updates the Constant Contact deprecation warning.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>6.0.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Removes unnecessary type declaration from nullable arguments to avoid deprecation warnings in PHP 8.4.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>6.0.1</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-601/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-601/</a></p>\n<h4>6.0</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-60/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-60/</a></p>\n<h4>5.9.7</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-597/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-597/</a></p>\n<h4>5.9.6</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-596/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-596/</a></p>\n<h4>5.9.5</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-595/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-595/</a></p>\n<h4>5.9.4</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-594/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-594/</a></p>\n<h4>5.9.3</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-593/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-593/</a></p>\n<h4>5.9.2</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-592/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-592/</a></p>\n<h4>5.9</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-59/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-59/</a></p>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:225:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/contact-form-7/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1176454\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/contact-form-7/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1176454\" alt=\"screenshot-1.png\"></a><p>screenshot-1.png</p></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:17403:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Sadly, no emails received (due to the rigid rules)</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 از 5 ستاره\" data-title-template=\"%s از 5 ستاره\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				توسط <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/taka-shi/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ec349e87931fcb6b985f5138b494b849565fa917865223536982fc8f48af6c82?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ec349e87931fcb6b985f5138b494b849565fa917865223536982fc8f48af6c82?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/taka-shi/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">TKO <small>(Taka-shi)</small></a> در <span class=\"review-date\">فوریه 17, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I noticed no email has been sent for these years. I spent a lot of time tweaking the Mail Setting due to the rigid rules that won\'t accept email addresses with different URLs, but nothing worked. I have switched to Ninja Forms. While my website using this plugin is not my primary one, I am so sad that I haven\'t received any emails because of this plugin. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Easy to use!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 از 5 ستاره\" data-title-template=\"%s از 5 ستاره\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				توسط <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/liviafalkner/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/868593ea989bcd66b7adfc5418076ece22dd1929b53bdafebd2445fede32ada0?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/868593ea989bcd66b7adfc5418076ece22dd1929b53bdafebd2445fede32ada0?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/liviafalkner/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Livia <small>(liviafalkner)</small></a> در <span class=\"review-date\">فوریه 17, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This plugin is really simple easy to use for the people who are starting with wordpress. 100% Recommended </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Best plugin for contact forms</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 از 5 ستاره\" data-title-template=\"%s از 5 ستاره\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				توسط <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/seller2222/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/56519afac53be7978d16223e9f895a406c25f1ef77e4e6b0cc0ea8fc1b168d57?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/56519afac53be7978d16223e9f895a406c25f1ef77e4e6b0cc0ea8fc1b168d57?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/seller2222/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">seller2222</a> در <span class=\"review-date\">فوریه 5, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I tried some other plugins, but <strong>Contact Form 7</strong> is the best.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Many thanks from WPHostee Team</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 از 5 ستاره\" data-title-template=\"%s از 5 ستاره\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				توسط <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/baicu4design/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/dd8f8591390e3f7e9b8f08c3df7879f0efb47bd3006f719f30223700ed6061c8?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/dd8f8591390e3f7e9b8f08c3df7879f0efb47bd3006f719f30223700ed6061c8?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/baicu4design/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">WPHostee <small>(baicu4design)</small></a> در <span class=\"review-date\">ژانویه 30, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Contact form 7 is an essential WordPress plugin, offering everything from top-notch security and performance improvements to social sharing tools and analytics. At WPHostee.com, our WordPress devs always install Contact Form 7 on every project we take on, as it’s a reliable tool that enhances the overall quality and functionality of our client sites.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Simple Contact Form</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 از 5 ستاره\" data-title-template=\"%s از 5 ستاره\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				توسط <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rizwanahmed007/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bcc5766baaf423c6834d7763bd2439e7dcdeb36585ef186f00f5b68ddabeea52?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bcc5766baaf423c6834d7763bd2439e7dcdeb36585ef186f00f5b68ddabeea52?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rizwanahmed007/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Rizwan Khan <small>(rizwanahmed007)</small></a> در <span class=\"review-date\">ژانویه 21, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I’ve been using <strong>Contact Form 7</strong> for years, and it’s undoubtedly one of the most reliable and versatile plugins for creating contact forms. Its simplicity, compatibility, and lightweight nature make it an excellent choice for WordPress users. The ease of customization and integration with other tools is impressive, and it has served my websites flawlessly.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>That said, I’d love to see a few enhancements to make this plugin even better. Adding a built-in date and calendar feature would simplify creating forms for bookings or appointments. Improving dropdown menu styling options would also be a great touch to enhance form aesthetics. Overall, this plugin remains a must-have for any WordPress site, and I look forward to seeing its future updates!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Simple yet Affective Contact Form.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 از 5 ستاره\" data-title-template=\"%s از 5 ستاره\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				توسط <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/danishalionline/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3874b75f6231dd375e4a6960595a54282269b39c5f644b94b3ff89d8e03cbd0e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3874b75f6231dd375e4a6960595a54282269b39c5f644b94b3ff89d8e03cbd0e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/danishalionline/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Danish Ali <small>(danishalionline)</small></a> در <span class=\"review-date\">ژانویه 9, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is the one plugin i used o my every wordpress site. its keeps getting better. However we would to see some more features like Calender and recapthca implementation with this form with ease. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Dude what happened</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 از 5 ستاره\" data-title-template=\"%s از 5 ستاره\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				توسط <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alexfreixa/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f9914f8f922eda27cc7167d52b1be04ee58300987cf4c48ed52c2f807eade773?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f9914f8f922eda27cc7167d52b1be04ee58300987cf4c48ed52c2f807eade773?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alexfreixa/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Alex Freixa <small>(alexfreixa)</small></a> در <span class=\"review-date\">ژانویه 3, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Why it\'s unusable? This plugin was working so fine. Customize it it\'s a nightmare!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Lack of support, lack of accessibility</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 از 5 ستاره\" data-title-template=\"%s از 5 ستاره\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				توسط <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/heggyy/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/84dd541d8963907b9e3fc8406d9e726f54649e658e5ce6d932e769a52e44f92f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/84dd541d8963907b9e3fc8406d9e726f54649e658e5ce6d932e769a52e44f92f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/heggyy/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">heggyy</a> در <span class=\"review-date\">ژانویه 3, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Overhyped plugin simply because it is free. It is the ultimate barebones of a plugin that people find necessary. There are no features, customizing anything means you are either a) a programmer or b) have to email support (in which case good luck getting help, egos too big). Gets no updates, no features, no accessibility or UX improvements. You\'re better off paying for a plugin than pulling your hair out to get it working as needed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">quick resposne to questions and support tickets</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 از 5 ستاره\" data-title-template=\"%s از 5 ستاره\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicon